途离开队伍，应该对超时后果有所预料，工作人员只是按规定办事，并无不妥。 「厕所卡」制度的初衷是为了维护排队秩序，保障大多数游客的游玩体验，这一点毋庸置疑。 但在实际操作中，20 分钟的时限是否合理，是否考虑到了游客的实际情况，例如女性、老人、小孩等特殊群体的生理需求，以及园区内厕所分布、排队情况等客观因素，这些都需要迪士尼方面进行考量和完善。 游客也应该提高规则意识，合理安排时间，预估潜在风险。 在明知有限时的情况下，可以选择错峰如厕，或与同行伙伴沟通好，避免超时带来的不便。同时，也应该对园区工作人员多一些理解和包容，毕竟他们也是在履行职责。女子迪士尼上厕所超时崩溃大哭，发放了厕所卡，限时 20 分钟 _ 游客 _ 时限 _ 网友"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-4ed1fdacd5786d416920fabab31fbe2e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "22 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664769973"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIk8abl5jX1PBMEAMaCTExMDAwNDA5NSCdqY+2BjAAOIoIQBdyCTY2NDc2OTk3M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1724191718.244541", "card_id": "Q_658427175", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "牛肉面怎么做最好吃?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "想给爸爸做，他特别喜欢吃李先生，有没有类似的，没有的话能不能把您觉得好吃的牛肉面教给我。谢谢您。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-c09862f3c1828317a9a86edf9da41b73_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "22 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658427175"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ik8abl5jX1PBMEAMaCTEwODU5NTE0NCD8nZGzBjAAOGBAGHIJNjU4NDI3MTc1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1724191718.244751", "card_id": "Q_413750439", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 123}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果手里存款足够，是否建议把房贷一次性还清？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-27d38893f311b606c110d6d56a9456d0_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "21 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "